data.title: Luna Davidova with the Spanish King Juan Carlos II and Queen Sofia
data.meta_description: This is a photo of some members of the Jewish community meeting with the Spanish King Juan Carlos II during his visit to Sofia in 1993. We met him and his wife, Queen Sofia, at the President's residence in Boyana. It was an interesting meeting. I liked him despite the fact that he was a representative of the same regime that drove away the Jews from Spain.
